      <title>由于美国和中国主要市场需求降温，星巴克下调年度销售预期</title>
      <link>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</link>
      <description><![CDATA[星巴克周二下调了年度销售预测，此前该公司报告称，由于其两大市场美国和中国对咖啡的需求疲软，同店销售额近三年来首次出现下滑。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.reuters.com/business/retail-consumer/starbucks-reports-surprise-fall-quarterly-sales-2024-04-30/</guid>
      <pubDate>Tue, 30 Apr 2024 20:10:52 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
